# Roblox server/client model
- Game state ONLY on ServerScriptService.
- Client handles UI, input, visual effects.
- RemoteEvents for client → server. RemoteFunctions for queries.
- Never trust client data. Validate everything server-side.

# Lua conventions
- Use local variables. Avoid globals.
- Module scripts return a table of functions.
- Consistent naming: PascalCase for modules, camelCase for functions.

# Maze generation
- Seeded RNG: seed = round ID for deterministic mazes.
- Grid-based: each cell has walls, items, spawn points.
- Generate on server, replicate to clients.

# Content guidelines
- Rating: 9+ (Mild). No blood, gore, or gambling.
- Follow Roblox Content Guidelines strictly.
- No external links or data collection.
